{"tid":83651,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)天煞異降 趕盡殺絕 怪獸與牠們的產地","createTime":"2017-01-17T02:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T07:01:03.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3eae6f03391a1baf7377054bb8bd3a310318c971","tid":83651,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:05:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=HAu269LU1Yhl9uyVLk7355kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e4bce72c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=HAu269LU1Yhl9uyVLk7355kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=7283aab5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog.hkmovie6.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/SOYL_D044_12364_rgb-678x381.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.hkmovie6.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FSOYL_D044_12364_rgb-678x381.jpg&h=606fbba1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.twword.com/uploads/wiki/6b/12/451943_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twword.com%2Fuploads%2Fwiki%2F6b%2F12%2F451943_1.jpg&h=a7c0376b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/94/Fantastic_Beasts_and_Where_to_Find_Them_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F94%2FFantastic_Beasts_and_Where_to_Find_Them_Poster.jpg&h=151c3a3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.神秘的太空船在全球多地降落現身，更發放不明訊息，人類安危遭受突發威脅！在無法辨別是敵是友的情況下，美國政府和軍方尋求語言學專家Louise（艾美亞當絲 飾）及科學家Scott（謝洛美維納 飾）的協助。二人必須在外星人再有行動前分析、拆解箇中玄機，然而過程中Louise腦海浮現出許多零碎的奇怪片段，當他們逐漸歸納出外星人來訪地球的真實目的，Louise赫然發現這些片段原來別有用意&hellip;&hellip;徘徊在世界存亡邊緣的人類，能否逃過一劫？<br />\n<br />\n2.某天晚上，無所事事的史密斯先生正坐在椅子上吃他最愛吃的紅蘿蔔，吃到一半突然看到一名男子正追殺著即將臨盆的孕婦，於是上前解救，這時才發現到原來追殺她的不只一位，而是一大群幫派分子，於是就在一陣槍林彈雨的情況下接生了這個孩子，等到史密斯先生想問清楚整個事情的來龍去脈，這名婦人已經中彈身亡了，於他帶著嬰兒逃離第一波槍戰..<br />\n<br />\n3.在1926年的紐約，英國巫師紐特&middot;斯卡曼德（Newt Scamander），他是一名古怪的奇獸飼育學家，他帶著看似其貌不揚的斑駁皮箱，乘小船經亞利桑那來到紐約市。到埗後，他遇到了瑪莉&middot;盧&middot;巴波（Mary Lou Barebone），她是一個沒有魔法的「麻瓜」（在美國稱為「莫魔」)，她領導的新塞勒姆慈善協會，它主張魔法世界裡有很多危險產生，巫師和女巫是真實而危險的。當紐特聽著她說話時，一隻奇怪生物從紐特的皮箱跑出來。當他試圖捕捉的時候，他意外地跟人掉換了皮箱。前正氣師波本蒂娜&middot;金坦這時以未註冊巫師的罪名逮捕了紐特，並帶他到美國MACUSA的總部，希望能重獲她的職位。然而，首長瑟拉菲娜&middot;皮奎里與魔法安全主任波西瓦&middot;葛雷夫斯撤銷案件。在雅各的公寓裡，幾個生物從紐特的手提箱逃脫..<br />\n<br />\n10 30AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b30f8492da5f0eadaa4f80bd923659508860f1c","tid":83651,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:10:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怪獸產地係北韓版"},{"pid":"8db967007859d848d5f6bfda91e7d5b9c7ceeb52","tid":83651,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怪獸產地係北韓版</blockquote><br />\n有興趣睇怪獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"475066b9cd2d8fb4a9343f8902768779f061d849","tid":83651,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa7db9f23bce508075ed1ad91b38b647ef8c812","tid":83651,"uid":2317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"手機睇唔到？ iOS"},{"pid":"3024a6ae602732b323ed0f64555f4a85ec214ff2","tid":83651,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockqu